HEADWORD: Unballast
<hw>Un*bal"last</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>ballast</ets>.]</ety> <def>To free from ballast;
